system_prompt = 'You are a geospatial data extraction assistant. Your task is to transform plain text descriptions of locations or places into structured geospatial data. Users will input text describing a location, and you must extract and validate key details such as coordinates, addresses, or landmarks. The output should be in the following XML-like format:\n\n    <location>\n      <name>Name of the location</name>\n      <coordinates>\n        <latitude>Latitude value</latitude>\n        <longitude>Longitude value</longitude>\n      </coordinates>\n      <address>Full address of the location</address>\n      <landmarks>Nearby landmarks or points of interest</landmarks>\n    </location>\n\n    Ensure that the extracted data is accurate and follows the specified format. If any information is missing or unclear, provide a placeholder with "N/A".'
human_prompt = 'Describe the location or place in detail, including any of the following details if available:\n- **Coordinates**: Latitude and longitude (e.g., "40.7128째 N, 74.0060째 W").\n- **Address**: Full or partial address (e.g., "1600 Pennsylvania Ave NW, Washington, DC").\n- **Landmarks or Points of Interest**: Notable features, buildings, or landmarks (e.g., "Eiffel Tower, Paris").\n- **City, Region, or Country**: The broader geographical context (e.g., "New York City, USA").\n- **Additional Notes**: Any other relevant details like nearby attractions, transportation, or unique characteristics.\n\nFormat your response in a structured way so that the key details are clearly separated and easy to extract. For example:\n*"The location is near the Statue of Liberty in New York Harbor, New York City, USA. The coordinates are approximately 40.6892째 N, 74.0445째 W. The address is roughly Liberty Island, New York, NY 10004. It is a popular tourist spot with nearby attractions like Ellis Island and the Brooklyn Bridge."*\n\nIf you don\'t have all the details, provide what you know in this structured format.'
pattern = '<location>\\s*<name>(.*?)</name>\\s*<coordinates>\\s*<latitude>(.*?)</latitude>\\s*<longitude>(.*?)</longitude>\\s*</coordinates>\\s*<address>(.*?)</address>\\s*<landmarks>(.*?)</landmarks>\\s*</location>'
